OL,5, The boss of P&O Ferries has said he is 
OL,6, "incredibly sorry" for the impact felt 
OL,7, by hundreds of staff who were recently 
OL,8, sacked by the company without notice.  
OL,10,FBut Peter Hebblethwaite insisted the   
OL,11,Fdecision was "the route we only deemed 
OL,12,Fpossible".                             
OL,14,FP&O Ferries sacked almost 800 seafarers
OL,15,Fin March and replaced them with foreign
OL,16,Fagency workers paid less than the      
OL,17,Fminimum wage.                          
OL,19,FThe move sparked outrage and led to    
OL,20,Fcalls for Mr Hebblethwaite to resign.  
